"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/65735","Home Office","false","2014-07-09","<p> </p><p>This matter remains under consideration. <br><br>In parallel, work continues on improving the efficiency of the process <br>including the introduction of an online system (eCommerce) which will be piloted in the <br>autumn and rolled out next year.</p><p> </p>","Lewes","Norman Baker","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/65735/answer",,,,,,"2014-07-09T15:18:39.0139444Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/65735/answer","Biography information for Norman Baker","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/65735/answer","Lewes","Norman Baker","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/65735/answer/previousversion/8940","Biography information for Norman Baker","1","Home Office","Home Office","2014-07-03","Firearms: Licensing","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, when she plans to bring forward proposals for reform of the firearms licensing fees system.","false","Biography information for Diana Johnson","Kingston upon Hull North","Diana Johnson","203943"
